        "TileImage": "$($repository f7cc77f9-1d1c-4fe1-a48d-7015f3352dbb).Image",
        "Description": "Daniel Romero and his friends refer to themselves as &quot;Children of the Corn.&quot;\r\rA group of kids played in the cornstalks, and spent their time in the Colorado dark laughing and sifting through the cornfields. However, one night, the group believed they saw a figure in leather, wearing gloves, wielding a sharp bloody sickle.\r\rTo ward off, the Children of the Corn wear green to resemble cornstalks, and watch out for it today.\r\rDaniel Romero and his friends should learn to stop searching, forever.",
